[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Imperfect</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Imperfect
<hw>Im*per"fect</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make imperfect.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Imperfectibility</ent>⟦br⟧
